TshisaLIVE spoke to Tira to find out his master plan for 2017.What is your resolution for 2017?I want to spend more time at the gym and with familyWhat is your one wish for 2017?My wish is to get more support from the private sector.If you had the power to change the world somehow, what would it be?I would like to see many artists getting opportunities.Your 2017 in one word will be...The best ever!